[01:52.46]He lifts the weak, He calls us friends
[01:56.79]Grace that starts and never ends
[02:01.12]The King of heaven walks with us
[02:05.46]All authority, all love, all trust
[02:09.79]Winds and waves know His voice
[02:14.12]Hearts awaken, we rejoice
[02:18.46]Kingdom come, let hope arise
[02:22.79]Heaven breaking through our lives
